Being part of the @bodyglove family is effin’ awesome!

Full edit in my bio!

node.text:
It’s the 1 percenters you do on a daily basis that will make the difference.
I’ve joined @myo.plant.nutrition #ICAN campaign and I’ve decided to challenge myself by being more environmentally conscious by picking up trash every time I’m on the lake, I’m also challenging myself to keep my body in better shape by foam rolling to start and finish my days! I invite you guys to join the #ICAN challenge just choose something you can improve on and hold yourself accountable for the next 2 weeks. 
We can all make a difference 
#theMYOChallenge #ad

node.text:
The LF drop 25 year heritage Limited graphic has been released! 
This is a massive part of not just LF’s history but the history of wakeboarding. Jimmy Redmond and Tony Finn designed the @liquidforcewake “Free” which at the time was the most progressive and futuristic board wakeboarding had seen. Thanks LF for choosing my board to print this graphic on, it’s an honor! 
Can’t wait to put these up on my wall 🙌🏻
